data.description: Stately full brick two story home with so much character and charm. Nearly an acre in desirable Meadow Lakes. Traditional floorplan with formal living and dining room that can also serve as home office or other purposes.  Primary suite is spacious with dual walk in closets and primary bath offers tile surround shower with glass door, tile flooring and granite countertop vanity.  Updated powder room has new sink, toilet and plank wood wall. Private, wooded yard with beautiful landscape lighting to make your evenings spent in the yard enjoyable. Fence has 2 10' gates and new 10x16x 7 shed. 2 car side load has great storage area. New septic tank replaced in 2019, 220 v in garage. *Seller is giving $5,000 incentive towards buyers closing cost.
